wiki.summary: Compilation of rare and out-of-print 7"s onto one 12" gatefold LP. Features lyrics, liner notes and pictures. Limited to 1000 copies. Tracks 1-2: Satanic Speed Metal 7" Tracks 3-4: King of Kings / Lord of the Wild 7" Tracks 5-7: ...Of Wolves, Women & War 7" Tracks 8-9: See You In Hell 7" There is a coloured edition only available from Kneel Before the Master's Throne Records and a special coloured tour-edition only available from the band at their European gigs. CD version released in Spring 2011 by Hells Headbangers Read more on Last.fm.
